  scenario="It is 2:15pm on a Thursday. You are halfway through laying engineered oak in a semi-detached in Harrogate — the boards are acclimatised, the underlay is down, and you have got a rhythm going on the click-lock installation. Your phone buzzes in your jacket across the room. A letting agent in Leeds has four rental properties that all need new LVT before new tenants move in next month — kitchens, hallways, and bathrooms. They want someone who can handle all four. Without AI Phone Answering, they hear your voicemail, assume you are too busy, and call the flooring company whose van they passed yesterday. With AI Phone Answering, they hear: 'Good afternoon, thank you for calling, how can I help?' The AI captures all four properties, the rooms involved, the timeline, and the agent's direct number. You finish the row at 3pm and call them back with a plan."
